                </div>
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <h1 class="hero-title">EXPRESSING EMOTIONS CAPTURING SOULS</h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">Every frame tells a story, feeling, moments that live forever.</p>
                    <button class="get-touch-btn">Get In Touch</button>
